item.title: Help please!
item.dc:creator: @Punkzombie Punkzombie
item.description:
@Punkzombie wrote:

are u running your server even? and if u took a source than just go into client.java (in the source not client) press ctrl+h and for the top textbox type in the other server or when u log in if it say welcome (something) type that in… for the buttom one type in ur server name do the same for the name and such than compile (if it doesnt work than get jdk, if it still doesnt work right-click ur compiler and u should see something like this C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java somewhere in there but after the jdk1.6.0_21 if it doesnt say ur version of java than change the 21 to ur version… (lastest version is 21) once u compile u can run ur server and play

for more tutorials go to http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/board,51.0.html and see what tutorials others have for u!
